lead_paragraph: Second-seeded Nick Kyrgios of Australia beat Inigo Cervantes of Spain 7-6 (4), 7-5 to advance to the quarterfinals of the Estoril Open on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Nick Kyrgios, Borna Coric in Quarterfinals of Estoril Open
